OPENCL version of the FDM code; to be run on GPU
===============================================

Prerequisites:
1) CUDA Toolkit Installed
2) MPI libraries with Fortran bindings

1) In the Makefile, set the following environment variables to appropriate compilers
MPIF90, MPICC , FF90 , CC, GCC

2) In the Makefile, set the following environment variables to MPI installation and CUDA toolkit installation directories respectively:
MPI_DIR, CUDA_HOME 

3) Running 'make' should compile the code

4) mpirun -np X ./disfd # would launch simulation with X processes
